Friday April 10, 2009

Alex talks with Master Mariner Captain Kelly Sweeney about the Somali pirate situation, William K. Black, the former senior regulator who cracked down on banks during the savings and loan crisis of the 1980s and appeared recently on the Bill Moyers Journal, and regular guest Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster. Alex takes on the issues of the day and also takes your calls.
